---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About this Portal" description="About Study Australia Org">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl text-primary mb-8">About this Portal</h1>
    <div class="font-body text-ink leading-relaxed">
      <p>留学澳洲综合（en，全球视角，跟 studyau.au 澳本地视角 + studyau.my 大马视角错开）</p>
      <p class="mt-4">This is an independent editorial site. We are not affiliated with any institution mentioned unless explicitly disclosed. Content is researched and written for informational purposes.</p>
      <p class="mt-4">Contact: <code>contact@studyau.org</code></p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>